[1] Sierra Leone: declared Ebola-free
Date: Mon 7 Dec 2015
Source: Blacknet, The Nubian Times report [edited]
http://www.blacknet.co.uk/sierra-leone-declared-ebola-free-watch


Sierra Leone has now officially been declared Ebola-free, after 42 days went by without a single case of the disease. The World Health Organisation (WHO) confirmed the news, which set [sic] the country into celebrations... -- more

