[5] Vaccine injury compensation - correction
[Re my comment in item [3] Vaccine, of Ebola update (131): WHO, semen, susp., prevention, blood, vaccine 20151203.3838759: "A compensation system for vaccine injuries is needed for diseases such as Ebola (http://medicalxpress.com/news/2015-12-compensation-vaccine-injuries-diseases-ebola.html), I misunderstood the suggestion to apply to survivors with post-Ebola syndrome, when in fact it only applies to post-vaccination injury. I withdraw my comment, and hope there will not be any undesirable long-term side effects from the vaccines. - Mod.JW]

